text: Tyrinthia frontalis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Félix Édouard Guérin-Méneville in 1855. It is known from Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Tyrinthia frontalis. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1855
